name: LOGO DESIGN
description:
Email - us@streetcodegpx.info with a description of how you want the LOGO to look and any images you want to include or are inspiration. Logo's are usually emailed to you with in 2-3 business days.

Typically with logos, we start with three or four mock logo design concepts for you to review. Out of those concepts I'll use your feedback to revise your favorite concept and work with you to perfect your desired final concept. 

To view more samples of Logo's visit: 
http://streetcodegpx.carbonmade.com
